{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2844 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2844 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2844","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'member' : cannot be a member of interface 'interface'","pos":[618,672]},{"pos":[679,817],"content":"An <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>interface class<ept id=\"p1\">](../../windows/interface-class-cpp-component-extensions.md)</ept> cannot contain a data member unless it is also a property.","source":"An [interface class](../../windows/interface-class-cpp-component-extensions.md) cannot contain a data member unless it is also a property."},{"content":"Anything other than a property or member function is not allowed in an interface.","pos":[824,905]},{"content":"Furthermore, constructors, destructors, and operators are not allowed.","pos":[906,976]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2844:","pos":[983,1020]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2844 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2844\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2844\"\nms.assetid: dcaf4cd2-21b0-4280-ae42-0a706c524d83\ncaps.latest.revision: 9\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2844\n'member' : cannot be a member of interface 'interface'  \n  \n An [interface class](../../windows/interface-class-cpp-component-extensions.md) cannot contain a data member unless it is also a property.  \n  \n Anything other than a property or member function is not allowed in an interface. Furthermore, constructors, destructors, and operators are not allowed.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2844:  \n  \n```  \n// C2844a.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr /c  \npublic interface class IFace {  \n   int i;   // C2844  \n   // try the following line instead  \n   // property int Size;  \n};  \n```  \n"}